  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps: 12-13 Guests</strong></p>
<p>Chalet Karin is located in a prime position in the centre of Arabba only 1 minute's (150m) walk from the nearest chair lift and only 3 minutes' walk (300m) from the main cable-car linking to the Sella Ronda. This delightful chalet is above a popular après-ski spot, ideal for guests looking for a lively and convenient base for their holiday. Chalet Karin is a well maintained modern chalet with great facilities include sociable dining area and separate living room upstairs with TV/DVD player and FREE Wi-Fi. All bedrooms have light wood furnishings and contemporary wooden floors, en suite shower and wc, satellite TV, safe and hairdryer.</p>]]></description>
